ery process for my\r\nrecent order, 88292.\r\n\r\nThe package failed to arrive within the timeframe promised at checkout, and\r\nI received no proactive communication regarding this delay. Reliable\r\ndelivery is a critical part of the shopping experience, and unfortunately,\r\nthis order fell well short of expectations.\r\n\r\nI would appreciate it if you could investigate why this delay occurred and\r\nprovide me with an update on when I can expect consistent service in the\r\nfuture.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nCharles Michael Carla\r\n', 'body_links': []}, {'message_id': '19dc60f52e5a0dd3', 'thread_id': '19dc60f52e5a0dd3', 'from': 'Carlos Miguel Carla <cm.carla03@gmail.com>', 'subject': 'Commendation for Great Service – [#88291]', 'date': 'Sun, 26 Apr 2026 03:12:53 +0800', 'internal_date': '1777144373000', 'label_ids': ['IMPORTANT', 'CATEGORY_PERSONAL', 'INBOX'], 'body': 'Dear Customer Service,\n\nI am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the assistance I\nreceived regarding my order 88291.\n\nI had a specific inquiry, and your representative handled it with\nremarkable professionalism and efficiency. It is rare to receive such\nhigh-quality support, and I wanted to ensure this positive experience was\nrecognized.\n\nThank you for your excellent service. It is a pleasure dealing with a team\nthat clearly values its customers.\n\nBest regards,\n\nCharles Michael Carla', 'has_attachments': False, 'attachments': [], 'body_full': 'Dear Customer Service,\r\n\r\nI am writing to express my sincere appreciation for the assistance I\r\nreceived regarding my order 88291.\r\n\r\nI had a specific inquiry, and your representative handled it with\r\nremarkable professionalism and efficiency. It is rare to receive such\r\nhigh-quality support, and I wanted to ensure this positive experience was\r\nrecognized.\r\n\r\nThank you for your excellent service. It is a pleasure dealing with a team\r\nthat clearly values its customers.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nCharles Mich